* phase-5 tail: DPS-8 binary floating-point DEC literals.  Each DEC value with
* a '.', E exponent, or D exponent assembles to a DPS-8 float word (8-bit
* two's-complement exponent + normalized two's-complement fraction); D doubles
* the mantissa to two words.  A trailing Bn binary-scales a fixed value.
       OUNAME FLTTEST
       DEC   1.5
       DEC   1E3
       DEC   -0.5
       DEC   1.0D0
       DEC   3B17
       END
